description: Are you in the driver's seat of your own career? In this FREE class you will learn inside tips and tricks from a recruiting and hiring professional! You'll walk away knowing what employers are doing to try and find you, how to be where they are and how to speak their language. It's 2016 and the job searching tactics of the past will no longer work. Sign up NOW for this FREE class, you won't regret it.
title: Find Your Dream Job
